---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <div class="home">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="headshot-wrap">
        <img src="/headshot.png" alt="Christina M. Bradley" />
      </div>

      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="section-label">PhD Candidate</p>
        <h1>Christina M. Bradley</h1>
        <p class="tagline">I study how emotions influence collaboration.</p>
        <div class="affiliation">
          <p>Department of Management &amp; Organizations<br />
          Stephen M. Ross School of Business<br />
          University of Michigan</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact">
          <a href="mailto:cmbrad@umich.edu">cmbrad@umich.edu</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="about">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <p>
        I am a PhD candidate in the Management and Organizations department at the University of
        Michigan's Ross School of Business. My research examines how responses to emotion
        expressions impact important workplace outcomes. I have developed a framework for
        understanding optimal emotional responses in challenging work contexts — including
        conflicts, negotiations, and workplace hierarchies.
      </p>
      <p>
        My recent work explores how individuals can express their emotions in ways that elicit
        more helpful responses. My dissertation, <em>Talking About Emotions Across Ranks: How,
        When, and Why it Improves Team Performance</em>, received the OB Division's nomination
        for the Academy of Management William H. Newman Award (2024 &amp; 2025) and is the
        recipient of the University of Michigan's Rackham Predoctoral Fellowship.
      </p>
      <p>
        My work has appeared in <em>Academy of Management Annals</em>, <em>Harvard Business
        Review Magazine</em>, <em>Harvard Business Review</em>, and <em>MIT Sloan Management
        Review</em>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="research-interests">
      <h2>Research Interests</h2>
      <p>
        My research focuses on (1) how individuals respond to the emotions of others and
        (2) how individuals express emotions in ways that enhance individual, relational, and
        team effectiveness. I am especially interested in emotion responding and expression in
        challenging situations, such as conflict and hierarchy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="highlights">
      <h2>Recent Highlights</h2>
      <ul class="highlight-list">
        <li>
          <strong>Finalist</strong> for the William H. Newman Award, Academy of Management (2025)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Rackham Predoctoral Fellowship</strong>, University of Michigan (2024–2025)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Best Reviewer Award</strong>, AoM Organizational Behavior Division (2024)
        </li>
        <li>
          Invited research talks at <strong>Harvard Business School</strong>, <strong>Rice University</strong>,
          and <strong>UT Austin McCombs</strong> (2024)
        </li>
        <li>
          Publication in <em>Academy of Management Annals</em> featured in
          <em>Harvard Business Review Magazine</em> (2024)
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .home {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */
  .hero {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .headshot-wrap {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .headshot-wrap img {
    width: 180px;
    height: 210px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-text {
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .hero-text h1 {
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }

  .affiliation {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contact a {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--navy-light);
  }

  /* ── Highlights ── */
  .highlight-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.7rem;
  }

  .highlight-list li {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .hero {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
